<sec>
<st>
Death</st>
<p>

Emerson died of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../271/865271.xml">
liver disease</link> aged 62 in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../849/53849.xml">
Hollywood, California</link>.  She was interred in Grace Hill Cemetery in her hometown.</p>

